{{!
    @template qtype_proforma/taskeditor_file

    The purpose of this template is to render a file in ProFormA task editor

    Classes required for JS:
    * none

    Data attributes required for JS:
    * none

    Context variables required for this template:
    * none

    Example context (json):
    {
        testid
        testname
    }


    Urspr端ngliche Klassen f端r das Top-Level-Div:
    class='ui-widget ui-widget-content ui-corner-all xml_file drop_zone'

    Urspr端ngliche Klassen f端r den Header:
    class='ui-widget-header'

